 factors can affect the effectiveness and accuracy of data analytics.\"", "\"VALUE IN DATA ANALYTICS\":\"Value refers to the benefits that Fruitee Co expects to gain from investing in data analytics. These benefits may be uncertain and difficult to measure.\"", "\"VOLUME IN DATA ANALYTICS\":\"Volume refers to the large amount of data that Fruitee Co could potentially analyze, including data about competitors, economic and social trends, retail sector developments, and customer feedback.\"", "\"VARIETY IN DATA ANALYTICS\":\"Variety refers to the different categories and types of data collected through Fruitee's systems. The data analytics capabilities need to classify and differentiate this variety to produce usable insights.\"", "\"VELOCITY IN DATA ANALYTICS\":\"Velocity refers to the speed at which new data is produced and collected. Fruitee Co's data analytics capabilities must deliver useful insights in a timely manner to support decision-making.\"", "\"VERACITY IN DATA ANALYTICS\":\"Veracity refers to the reliability and accuracy of the underlying data. Fruitee Co needs to ensure that its data collection methods capture accurate and timely data.\""], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-3-small", "temperature": 0.0, "frequency_penalty": null, "presence_penalty": null, "top_p": 1.0, "max_tokens": 4000, "n": 1}}